        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "You can now modify existing SPF/PC panels to customize operations"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "to suit local conditions. You can also extend SPF/PC by adding new"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "functions to the primary option panel along with their respective"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "panel trees."
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "SPF/PC faithfully emulates ISPF Dialog Services Panel Definition"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "Language. We support the ISPF process model and most major services"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "so in many cases you will be able to download your mainframe panels"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "and run them without modification."
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "For further details see:"
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "SPF/PC User Guide and Reference,"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "Panel Definition ............... Page 8-1"
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "SPF/PC Command Reference"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "ISPEXEC Dialog Services ........ Page 3-1"
      }
    ]
  },
